Hi, and welcome back to Line Sheet. Today, Rachel Strugatz
digs into what=E2=80=99s really happening at Glossier, the beauty brand (or=
 maybe just the brand?) of our time. Up top, some C-suite news from Saks Gl=
obal, and my final thoughts on the final New York shows.

I=E2=80=99ve had a fabulous past 24 hours here. Yesterday afternoon, I wore=
 a hard hat to walk through the new Laura Gonzalez=E2=80=93designed Printem=
ps department store at 1 Wall Street, set to open this spring, just a block=
 away from
